OL,3,CFlood deaths 'caused by sewer network'
OL,5,FFlooding on a road where a couple
OL,6,Fdrowned was caused by issues with the
OL,7,Fsewer network, according to a report.
OL,9,FElaine Marco, 76 and her husband
OL,10,FPhilip, 77 died after their black
OL,11,FMercedes was submerged in water on
OL,12,FQueen's Drive in Liverpool on 26
OL,13,FAugust 2023.
OL,15,FThe independent report by Liverpool
OL,16,FCity Council found that the sewer
OL,17,Fnetwork could not cope with heavy
OL,18,Frainfall.
OL,20,FThe couple died just days before their
OL,21,F54th wedding anniversary.
