OL,3,CFlood deaths 'caused by sewer network'
OL,5,FEmergency services were called to four
OL,6,Fother incidents of vehicles being
OL,7,Fsubmerged in floodwater in the months
OL,8,Fleading up to the deaths of Elaine and
OL,9,FPhilip Marco, according to the report.
OL,11,FOn two occasions, people had to be
OL,12,Frescued from their vehicles.
OL,14,FAll of the incidents took place when
OL,15,Fyellow or amber weather warnings for
OL,16,Feither heavy rain or thunderstorms
OL,17,Fwere issued.
