OL,3,CFlood deaths 'caused by sewer network'
OL,5,FAccording to the report, an
OL,6,Finvestigation into the flooding and
OL,7,Fhydraulic modelling carried out by
OL,8,Fwater company United Utilities showed
OL,9,F"surcharging of the sewer network"
OL,10,Fduring heavy rainfall was the primary
OL,11,Fcause of the flooding.
OL,13,FCommissioned with engineering firm
OL,14,FMott Macdonald, the report said
OL,15,Fmembers of the public reported a
OL,16,F"plume of water" gushing out of the
OL,17,Fsewer's inspection chamber, where the
OL,18,Fmanhole cover had blown, causing the
OL,19,Fwater level to rise "extremely
OL,20,Fquickly".
