OL,3,CFlood deaths 'caused by sewer network'
OL,5,FIt said: "Due to the force of the
OL,6,Fwater emanating from the public sewer
OL,7,Fthis caused an almost tidal effect
OL,8,Fwithin the flood water."
OL,10,F"The combined sewer network in the
OL,11,Farea cannot cope with the volume of
OL,12,Fwater that falls in a short period of
OL,13,Ftime."
OL,15,FThe highway drainage system
OL,16,Fcontributed to the flood, it found.
OL,18,FThe frequency of flooding incidents
OL,19,Fwas noted to have risen in 2023, with
OL,20,Fthe cause still to be verified.
