OL,5,FThe report recommended United
OL,6,FUtilities, along with the council and
OL,7,FNetwork Rail, work to find permanent
OL,8,Fsolutions to reduce the frequency and
OL,9,Fimpact of flooding in the area.
OL,11,FSince the fatal incident, Liverpool
OL,12,FCity Council has installed measures
OL,13,Fincluding sensors which provide early
OL,14,Fwarnings of rising water levels, CCTV
OL,15,Fcameras, signage and road barriers.
OL,17,FIn a statement after their deaths, the
OL,18,Ffamily of the Marcos said the "only
OL,19,Fcomfort" was that they were together
OL,20,Fto the end.
